Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">《Trap Rap》</span></span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">更细一点的风格，也是能通过</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">对鼓点</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">和<strong>氛围的描述</strong>来实现，比如说让他做一首 Drill 风格的 Beat（有点内味儿了）：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(122, 121, 121);line-height: 24px;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3390822168049106951" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5gR6KWHNb7TPuTNMgDd9wvggHOxXpicueKNliaptZLI6qxkANjYicgHwAgJ6qPCYpOSyFFNxPdzNOQqgaz2LE0YOQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-w="512" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3390822168049106951"></iframe><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 14px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);">🎵</span>《Drill Rap》</span></p><p style="visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 12px 36px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(244, 243, 240);color: rgb(43, 42, 42);line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">将<strong>邓典果</strong>的《Test》这首歌的歌词填到这个 Beat，还是挺贴的：</span></p><p style="text-align: c